node.text:
I’ve gone back and forth over the last week on whether or not I wanted to share this story I posted to my feed... after messaging back and forth with so many of you who feel exactly what I feel, who feel the pain I’ve felt many times over... today it’s important for me to share this message one more time

There’s always some standard of beauty that you’re not meeting. ‘Cause if you’re thin enough then you don’t have that ass that everyone wants. But if you have enough weight on you to have an ass, then your stomach isn’t flat enough. It’s all just ... impossible -Taylor Swift

Everyday there is someone online who feels the need to leave me a nasty comment or send me a CRUEL direct message or repost me to their story to exemplify something they do not agree with

I am SO sick and tired of strangers online telling us HOW we should look, WHAT we should eat... last week I was too thin and this week I’m overweight, bloated and don’t look “fit” enough. I’m done

You. Are. Enough... and nobody should EVER make you feel like less of a person or make you question who you are or what you look like. We are so blessed to live inside this AMAZING body that holds us, allows us to walk and talk and breathe. Our body takes care of us so we need to take care of it INSTEAD OF constantly beating ourselves up for not meeting a standard of beauty strangers and society might place on us

So the next time you feel like you’re not enough, I hope my words can uplift you. I choose to be nothing but a positive light to you because in a world of so much hatred, negativity and cruel people and words... WHY ADD TO IT? Be a light and do not let ANYONE dim it. Please continue to shine and uplift others because we need more incredible women like you in this world!!! I love you. It’s a beautiful day to be alive💫

node.title: There’s ALWAYS some standard of beauty you’re NOT meeting✨

DO IT WITH ME! 6 MINUTE ab workout babyyyy 😅💦 using absolutely nothing but YOU... quick, simple and trust me lmao your core will be on HOT FIRE

7 EXERCISES
30S ON 20S REST

1️⃣ sprinter crunches
2️⃣ high plank around the worlds
3️⃣ swimmer crunches with single leg tuck in
4️⃣ feet together sit ups
5️⃣ low plank spider crunch
6️⃣ high side plank oblique crunch right
7️⃣ high side plank oblique crunch left

Rest 60S and if you’re up for it, LETS DO IT AGAIN👏🏼 Repeat circuit 2-3x 😩

COME TRAIN WITH ME✨ download my app @alivebywhitney and try it out free for 7-days!! My new AT HOME program ALIVE INSIDE just launched on the app🤍

node.text:
4-5 weight training sessions a week with 2-3 rest days! One of those rest days is usually a hot yogaaaaa day 🧘🏼‍♀️✨ currently training abs 1-3 times a week and for cardio... you know the drill 😅💦 1-2 HIIT sessions a week

I’ve learned to be more flexible with my workout schedule!! Life happens and sometimes I miss a workout or need to shift some workouts around and that’s OK👏🏼 be sure to give your body the rest and recovery it needs and most importantly, create a workout split that makes YOU happy and will push you to get your cute bum to the gym 🥰❤️

node.text:
BOOTY DEMOLITION 🥵❤️‍🔥 here are 3 accessory exercises to add to your next leg workout to get your glutes feeling on FIRE 🔥😮‍💨 LEGS GOO

1️⃣ 3x10 landmine single leg hip thrusts each leg 🔥 feel free to swap the landmine out for a dumbbell here

2️⃣ 3x5 bulgarian split squat to single leg RDL 💦 each movement is 1 rep and it’s a TOUGH ONE

3️⃣ 3x12 dumbbell frog pumps babyy

node.text:
BACKKKK ATTACK baby 😮‍💨🥵❤️‍🔥 here’s a complete PULL WORKOUT that left me feeling roasty and toastyyyy 👏🏼 feeling so good let’s GET AFTER IT

Train with me on @alivebywhitney 💙 download my app Alive for my at-home and gym training programs

1️⃣ 4 sets of conventional deads 🥵 with each set, reps went down and weight went up 👏🏼 10, 8, 6 then 4
2️⃣ 3x8 bent over single-arm row
3️⃣ 3x6 alternating static hold curls
4️⃣ superset: 3 sets
10 straight arm pull downs
12 cable hammer curls
5️⃣ 3x10 lat pull down

Wearing @gymsharkwomen
Song is Memory by Kane Brown

DUMBBELL ONLY LEG WORKOUT for my shy girlies, beginners or if you’re working out from home 🥰

CLAIM YOUR BENCH
GRAB YOUR DUMBBELLS
and complete this entire workout from one spot 👏🏼💦 this is how I started out when I first started lifting and wasn’t the ~most~ comfortable yet. Soon enough you’ll feel ready to venture out a bit more in the gym. You’ve got this 🌈🌸🤍 @alivebywhitney

node.text:
3-INGREDIENT SNACKADILLA 🍌🤎🤤 it’s quick, SUPER EASY and ITSAAA 10 out of 10 for me 🥵

1️⃣ slice up a banana 🍌 I only ended up using half of it for the SNACKADILLA
2️⃣ top half of a tortilla - I used almond flour @sietefoods tortilla ofc 🤎 with peanut 🥜 butter
3️⃣ add your sliced banana and cinnamon and cook to desired crunchiness
4️⃣ finish off with some chocolate 🍫 chips if you want but then it’ll make this 4-ingredients, not 3 😂

LMK what I should try next ❤️‍🔥 BIG thank you to @shapedbycharlotte for this one

QUAD DEMOLITION 🥵😮‍💨❤️‍🔥 here are 3 accessory exercises to add to your next leg day to help ROAST and TOAAAST your quads 🔥 LEGSS GOOO

1️⃣ 3 sets of 12
dumbbell sissy squats

2️⃣ 3 sets of 10
front rack open stance lunges

banded single-leg leg extensions. banded is a good alternative if you don’t have access to the machine ❤️‍🔥

DON’T HAVE ANY TIME FOR THESE PEOPLE HIIT WORKOUT 😩✋🏼 run into your ex on the street?? Simple HUT HIKE away 💦

Complete each exercise for 40 seconds, followed by a 20 second rest and repeat 🔁 circuit 5x 😮‍💨

Trend credit to @j.banks54 🙏🏼 check him out for some FIRE content ❤️‍🔥

KICKING OFF the week with this HOT HOT FIRE 🥵 leg and Glute workout 😮‍💨❤️‍🔥 feeling roasted and toasted after this one.. LEGSS GET IT

1️⃣ 4x5-8 barbell squats
2️⃣ 3x10 landmine single-leg hip thrust
3️⃣ 3x5 bulgarian split squat to single-leg RDL 💦 this movement requires a lot of stabilization so separate the two movements or do it assisted if this is too difficult right now ❤️‍🔥

4️⃣ 4x5 barbell pause hip thrusts
5️⃣ 3x12 glute medius cable kickbacks
6️⃣ 2x15 dumbbell sissy squats using @califullerfit band 🌈

TRAIN WITH ME on Alive 💦💙 download my app @alivebywhitney for my at-home and gym programs

Wearing @gymsharkwomen
Song is u love u by blackbear
